### What to do when new release of NuTyX is done:

1. Rsync the depots of x86_64:

rsync -av --delete .rolling/ .fixed/

2. Makes the appropriates links:

ln -svf .fixed <new_version> in x86_64
ln -svf .rolling <new_version> in i686

3. Make the ISOS

4. Change the registration validation string on both forums 

5. Replace  the <old_version> string to <new_version> string on nutyx.org website

6. Make the news on both forums

7. Make the news with following template:

   7.1  NuTyX <new_version> disponible avec cards <version>
   7.2  Liste des mises à jour principales
   7.3  Procédure de mise à jour
   7.4  Points spécifiques à cette version
   7.4.1 ....
   7.4.2 ...
   7.4.n ..
   7.5  Anciennes nouvelles

8. adjust wikipedia version
